title: Yes - Keys To Ascention - Live (resequenced by }{eywood)
description:
Yes 
Keys to Ascension
The concert


This is a mix of the tracks from the CDs and the DVD audio.  I stuck mostly to the CDs for true lossless content, reverting to the DVD only when necessary to grab a transition.  One of my easier projects, this made K2A into a double live album and a studio album. The studio album is commercially available as Keystudio, so no need for me to release my version here.
